name: Cotopaxi Uyuni 46L Duffle Bag - Del Dia - Unisex
description: On your next trip, pack a duffle that's down for adventures. This versatile bag lays flat, stands on end, and is easy to carry thanks to the stowable shoulder strap and 5 grab handles. It's also got a laptop sleeve, a laundry compartment and a zippered pocket to keep you organized. And you'll always know which duffle is yours at baggage claim: as part of Cotopaxi's Del Día collection, the Uyuni is made with remnant materials by sewers who have creative control over its final look. No two packs are alike.Made with durable 420-denier nylon, and 210-denier nylon ripstop in areas that see less wear to save weight. Both are sourced from fabric remnants.Padded shoulder strap to carry it cross-body. Stow it away when you don't need it.5 reinforced handles for pulling it out of the trunk or off luggage carousels.Full-length top zipper has a protective webbing flap.Padded laptop sleeved with side access zipper.Zippered top pocket and collapsible laundry pocket add organization.
